<h5>Wednesday 22 May 2013 at <strong>17:30</strong></h5><h1><span class="pale">Law and Finance Seminar Series</span><br />Executive Retirement Pay and Incentives</h1><p>Speaker: <strong>Robert Jackson</strong>, Associate Professor of Law, Columbia Law School</p><p>Venue: <a href="http://www.law.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Oxford Law Faculty</a> The Cube</p><p class="newsflash">For more information please  contact: <a href="mailto:oxlfevents@law.ox.ac.uk">Oxford Law and Finance Events</a></p><hr /><p>Interested in this subject? View our <a href="/subject/62">Law and Finance</a> page.</p><div class='dotted-top-border'><p><a href="http://denning.law.ox.ac.uk/news/events_files/ExecutiveRetirementPayandIncentives.pdf">Full Text Paper</a></p></div><div class='dotted-top-border'><p><a href="http://denning.law.ox.ac.uk/news/events_files/Robert_Jackson_bio.pdf">Robert Jackson Bio</a></p></div><div class="dotted-top-border"><p>Part of the <a href="/news/discussiongroup.php?group=LFSS">Law and Finance Seminar Series</a></p></div><hr /><p><a href="/events.php">Show all forthcoming events</a> or <a href="javascript:history.back()" title="does the same as using your browser's Back button">go back one page</a></p><!-- InstanceEndEditable -->


